### User-Service Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health
Accept: application/json

### Get User-Service Status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/status
Accept: application/json

### Import Users from Excel (Step 1: REQUIRED)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users/import/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-users.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./test-data/test-users.xlsx
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Get Import Status by Event ID (use eventId from previous response)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/import/status/evt_test_123
Accept: application/json

### List All Users (verify they were created)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users
Accept: application/json

### Get Single User Details
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/usr_test_001
Accept: application/json

### Get Users by Role (should all be OCCUPANT)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users?role=OCCUPANT
Accept: application/json

### Get Verified Users Only (should all be true)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users?isVerified=true
Accept: application/json
